			"updated": 1774767569216,
			"link": null,
			"locked": false,
			"text": "```java\nboolean[] isPrime = new boolean[n+1];  \nArrays.fill(isPrime, true);                  \nisPrime[0] = isPrime[1] = false;          \n\nfor(int i=2; i*i<=n; i++) {                  \n    if(isPrime[i]) {                          \n        for(int j=i*i; j<=n; j+=i) {          \n            isPrime[j] = false;              \n        }\n    }\n}",
			"rawText": "```java\nboolean[] isPrime = new boolean[n+1];           \nArrays.fill(isPrime, true);                     \nisPrime[0] = isPrime[1] = false;                \n\nfor(int i=2; i*i<=n; i++) {                    \n    if(isPrime[i]) {                            \n        for(int j=i*i; j<=n; j+=i) {           \n            isPrime[j] = false;                \n        }\n    }\n}",
			"fontSize": 20,
			"fontFamily": 5,
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": null,
			"originalText": "```java\nboolean[] isPrime = new boolean[n+1];           \nArrays.fill(isPrime, true);                     \nisPrime[0] = isPrime[1] = false;                \n\nfor(int i=2; i*i<=n; i++) {                    \n    if(isPrime[i]) {                            \n        for(int j=i*i; j<=n; j+=i) {           \n            isPrime[j] = false;                \n        }\n    }\n}",
			"autoResize": false,
			"lineHeight": 1.25,
			"hasTextLink": false
		},
